Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:05.12,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:122247,125125}Hm? Captain's fallen behind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.58,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:125125,126585}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:09.42,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:126585,129421}Maybe she takes a rest\Nsomewhere again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:129421,131632}There's something off\Nabout her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:131632,134009}It's the last day of our trip…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.01,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:134009,136011}Maybe she sat down\Nbecause her wound hurts so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.84,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:136011,136845}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.68,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:136845,139681}I asked her about it this morning\Nand she said it's not that bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.30,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:139681,141308}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:141308,142142}But?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.93,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:142142,143935}She said she's feeling a bit weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:35.61,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:152861,155614}It's only natural.\NIt's her first trip in a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:39.49,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:155614,159493}She must've built up a lot of stress\Nin the spring tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.74,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:159493,162746}Yeah, besides, we just played\Nagainst the Mighty Six. You can't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.16,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:162746,164164}Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.70,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:164164,165707}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:48.12,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:165707,168126}– Captain!\N– Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:53.54,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:169836,173548}Why do I feel so weak\Nfrom the morning today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:173548,177678}Honestly, I'd love to turn back\Nand just stay in bed all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:03:00.68,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:177678,180681}But I'd worry the girls if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.26,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:180681,182265}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:182265,184476}I'm going, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.90,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:192275,194903}Kozue, is your leg really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:194903,197406}Yes, it is.\NI'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:197406,198782}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:22.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:198782,202285}We're almost at the summit.\NJust one last push. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:23.07,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:202285,203078}– Yeah!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:208667,209626}Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.29,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:211461,213296}Heave-ho!\NWhew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.50,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:213296,215507}Looks like our Chief has recovered.\NShe's the first again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.39,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:227894,229396}We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:231231,233108}What a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:234192,236653}It was tough,\Nbut I'm glad we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:237446,239656}You can see Nara from here.{NOTE:奈良市}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.07,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:242826,245078}Huh? Even though it's that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.08,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:245078,247080}Yes. It seems that's really it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:12.16,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:247080,252169}We have come a long way,\Nmuch further than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.62,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:252169,254629}We're near the prefectural border.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.71,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:254629,256715}Look, you can see Suzuka over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:20.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:256715,260093}And behind that mountain,\Nit's Ōsaka and Jidōin High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:25.01,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:260093,265015}Now that you mention it, didn't the Mighty Six\Nhave some business in Suzuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:265015,266057}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.25,Default,Biker,0,0,0,,{TIME:298006,299257}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:319236,321780}At first I thought they're\Njust a bunch of delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:321780,324157}But Maya had this\Nmysterious charm around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.16,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:324157,327160}She had this inner restlessness,\Npushing her to find new challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:328995,330997}Kozue, why are you spacing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:35.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:330997,335293}I wasn't thinking about anything in particular.\NI was only admiring scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:335293,338630}That's fine, but you haven't eaten\Neven a single onigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:340924,343510}I have no appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:343510,344594}Kozue…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.42,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:344594,346429}Chief, is it because\Nof your injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:346429,347931}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:347931,349432}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:349432,350934}Leaving that aside…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.01,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:350934,352018}Yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:355313,356648}I-I'll have an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.56,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:356648,358567}Okay! I'll give you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.77,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:358567,360777}But could you give me\Nyour onigiri in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:360777,362779}Sure. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:03.86,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:362779,363864}It was too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.79,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:374332,375792}Oh my god, a lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.21,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:375792,378210}Thunderstorms in the mountains\Ncan be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.21,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:378210,379212}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.55,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:386511,387554}Let's get to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.63,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:387554,388638}C-C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:388638,390390}Ishimatsu, don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:390390,392475}Don't forget your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.76,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:392475,394769}– It got dark so fast!\N– Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:47.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:406573,407616}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.28,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:413413,414289}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:58.16,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:414289,418168}It's going to start raining on the way.\NIt'll be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.17,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:424174,426176}We need to find a shelter somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.42,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:426176,428428}But we're in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:428428,430180}It hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:437062,438271}Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.85,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:438271,440857}– Captain!\N– Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.98,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:440857,443985}Kozue, what's going on?\NHang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:443985,445904}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.15,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:445904,447155}She has terrible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.90,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:447155,448907}Is it because of her injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.74,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:452327,453745}What if…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:453745,455997}What if, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.12,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:455997,458124}What if…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.58,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:458124,459584}Talk to me, Makimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.62,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:460752,462629}There's someone coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.71,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:465423,466716}Ah! Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.46,Default,Hiker,0,0,0,,{TIME:466716,468468}What are you girls doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.17,Default,Hiker,0,0,0,,{TIME:468468,470178}You should get to a shelter soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.34,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:470178,471346}One of us is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.59,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:471346,473598}Can you tell us where the next village is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:58.56,Default,Hiker,0,0,0,,{TIME:473598,478561}If you go down the mountain, there is one about\Nan hour from here. But they have no hospital there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.73,Default,Hiker,0,0,0,,{TIME:480689,483733}Oh, right. There is a medical shelter\Nfrom the University of Ōsaka nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:07.94,Default,Hiker,0,0,0,,{TIME:483733,487946}They also have a pharmacy, and there's a doctor.\NBut I'm not sure if he's working today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.82,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:487946,489823}That's great!\NWhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:491199,492534}Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.70,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:492534,493702}Chief…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:494411,496246}It hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.08,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:496246,498081}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.65,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:530196,531656}Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.21,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:542542,544210}Oh, I see you need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.29,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:544210,547297}Luckily, today there is\Na university doctor on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.92,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:547297,548923}Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.30,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:548923,551301}Unfortunately,\Nyou'll have to wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.30,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:551301,554304}He was called down to the village\Nfor an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.80,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:555722,558808}Anyway, please come in.\NLet's get your friend on bed for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.93,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:558808,559934}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.32,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:571488,573323}Makimura-san, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:37.82,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:573323,577827}Your father is a doctor.\NYou know what's happening to Kozue, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.41,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:577827,579412}Hey, if you do, please tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.95,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:579412,581956}What if Chief…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.64,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:597847,598640}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:598640,600183}Hang in there, Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:00.89,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:600183,600892}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:08.73,Alternative,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:605730,608733}There's no way that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.23,Alternative,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:608733,611236}Ayuhara-san's…\NNo, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.53,Alternative,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:611236,613530}I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.57,Alternative,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:613530,615573}Please, let me be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.57,Alternative,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:615573,618576}God, I'm begging you.\NDon't let me be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:23.87,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:621329,623873}The manager told me you're here.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.88,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:631256,632882}Doctor!\NAyuhara-san is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.96,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:634592,635969}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.76,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:635969,638763}Alright, girls.\NStay calm and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.68,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:642642,644686}It's tetanus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:57.32,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:653486,657323}It's quite serious,\Nbut we don't have an antitoxin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.24,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:657323,659242}I'll contact nearest hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:660285,662662}What happens\Nif she doesn't get treated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.16,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:662662,664164}She's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.62,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:664164,666624}W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.30,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:676926,679304}Hello?\NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.22,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:679304,681222}Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.84,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:681222,682849}I can't hear you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.76,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:682849,684767}Huh!?\NA landslide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.06,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:684767,686060}What about a helicopter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:29.43,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:686060,689439}Cut the crap!\NIf she doesn't get it, she'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.27,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:689439,691274}Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.27,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:691274,693276}Alright.\NLet's try the faculty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.53,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:697488,699532}Hello?\NHello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.78,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:699532,700783}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:47.91,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:703369,707916}There was a landslide on the way to Yagyū Highway\Nfrom Nara City and the road has been blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.16,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:707916,710168}Helicopters can not take off\Nin this storm either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.46,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:712587,714464}I was about to call Ōsaka University.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.59,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:714464,716591}But looks like the landline was cut, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:05.85,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:720220,725850}Doctor, Chief… Ayuhara-san… is she really going\Nto die if she doesn't get the antitoxin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.35,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:725850,728353}Please do something, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.18,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:728353,730188}I could cut out the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:13.27,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:730188,733274}But in her condition I would have to\Namputate the leg below the knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.69,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:733274,734692}Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:19.03,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:734692,739030}But if we're lucky,\Namputation could save her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:24.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:739030,744535}But if Kozue can't play volleyball anymore,\Nshe'll be devastated beyond imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:28.16,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:744535,748164}There's still hope.\NYou can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.32,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:777485,779320}Hey, do you have a death wish!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.61,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:780071,783616}C-Captain… Captain is…\NOur captain is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:06.24,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:783616,786244}Captain?\NAyuhara Kozue?
Comment: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:11.79,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:791791,791791}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.64,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:806597,807640}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.68,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:809892,812687}She got a sedative injection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.85,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:812687,814856}But she can still feel the pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:38.56,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:814856,818568}If we do not do anything, her respiratory system\Nwill be affected next and she will suffocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.15,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:818568,820153}We have to get her the antitoxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:46.70,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:822405,826701}How much time do we have\Nbefore she has to take the drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:50.28,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:826701,830288}The sooner the better.\NI would say that the midnight is the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.70,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:830288,832707}We can't wait any further than that.\NEvery minute counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.37,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:832707,835376}After that I have to amputate\Nand hope she pulls through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.88,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:836377,838880}I'll bring you the antitoxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:13:59.67,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:838880,839672}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.30,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:841299,845303}Have you gone mad? There's a terrible storm\Nout there, and the road to Nara is shut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.97,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:845303,848973}It'll be fine.\NI'll go to Ōsaka through Suzuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:16.02,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:852310,856022}Please promise me, Doctor, that you\Nwon't amputate the leg before 12 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.52,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:856022,858524}I understand.\NTake this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:28.40,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:864197,868409}I trust you, Doctor. If you cut it before\Nthe promised time, you will regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.49,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:868409,869494}Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.70,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:869494,870703}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.53,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:870703,872538}All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.95,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:872538,873956}– Yeah!\N– 'Aight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:51.97,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:890765,891974}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:17.64,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:972597,977643}If all went according to the plan, they should've\Nreached the medical university by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:15.11,Default,Chemist,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030488,1035117}All right. I'll make sure an ambulance\Ngets the drug there as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.86,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035117,1036869}It won't reach them\Nbefore midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.08,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036869,1039080}Please give it to me.\NI'll deliver it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.62,Alternative,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040081,1042625}Three and half an hour…\NIt took longer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:25.71,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042625,1045711}We go at full speed.\NGot that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.83,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1045711,1046837}– Yeah!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.92,Default,Chemist,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046837,1047922}Fine, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.59,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047922,1049590}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.13,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049590,1052134}Okay, let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.17,Default,Tamiya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088170,1090172}I'll hold them back.\NHurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.25,Default,Kasagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133174,1134258}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.01,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179845,1181013}Tani…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.26,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181013,1182264}Tobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.72,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183557,1185726}We're fine.\NTake this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.41,Alternative,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209625,1211419}It's over, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.01,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220094,1221011}Kozue, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.53,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280821,1282531}You're… Tsutomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.53,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282531,1284533}Tsutomu-kun, please answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:25.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284533,1285659}Tsutomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.53,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285659,1287536}Tsutomu-kun,\NI want to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:29.87,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287536,1289872}Don't come here.\NKozue, stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.37,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289872,1292374}Don't come to the light!\NIt's too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292374,1293918}Tsutomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.71,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293918,1296712}Tsutomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.29,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296712,1298297}Tsutomu-kun…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:47.64,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305930,1307640}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.01,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307640,1309015}Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:49.97,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309015,1309975}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314688,1315606}Ishimatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:00.48,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318442,1320486}She didn't make it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:22.75,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340297,1342758}Ayuhara Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.38,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342758,1345386}Don't die.\NDon't you dare dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:02.54,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381338,1382548}Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.17,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382548,1384174}Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:05.38,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384174,1385384}Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:08.55,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385384,1388554}The Mighty Six\Nkeep their promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:12.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391557,1392975}Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:16.43,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394435,1396437}Hurry up and take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.45,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1415205,1416457}We made it in time, huh.
Comment: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:00.43,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1440439,1440439}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:07.15,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443150,1447154}Thanks to the on-time delivery\Nof the antitoxin, Kozue's life is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:10.53,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1447154,1450532}This success wouldn't happen\Nif it wasn't for Maya's great effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:12.53,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1450532,1452534}Maya walks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:17.58,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452534,1457581}When Kozue learns of it,\Nshe begins to think about Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:21.16,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1457581,1461168}One day, a boy appears before Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.16,0:24:25.75,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1461168,1465756}He evokes in Kozue feelings\Nthat vaguely remind her of Tsutomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.75,0:24:28.46,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1465756,1468467}Please look forward to the next episode.
Comment: 0,0:24:30.46,0:24:30.46,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1470469,1470469}Ending
